title: Taboo | On The Sands Of Serkonos
author: Real Scorsese
comment: As a huge fan of both Taboo and Dishonored, I can say this must be one of the best mashups ever! :D
I love this song in the Dishonored 2.

When I first played Dishonored, I immediately thought about Taboo. The story with this whole political intrigue and the industrial city of Dunwall which was like England in the 1800s reminded me this amazing series. It seems that I wasn't the only one who noticed the similarities. Great work!
description: Montage video for the series "Taboo" with Tom Hardy.
